'''2.3.549''' is an update to the [[Minecraft Launcher|launcher]] released on December 19, 2022.

== Additions ==
* Added information for new year's celebration.

== Changes ==
* Updated player-facing error message linking flow.

== Fixes ==
* Fix to game launch problem for Minecraft Java versions below 1.19 on Mac.
* {{bug|MCL-21767}} - Launcher strings fail to capitalize brand-names.</onlyinclude>
